example_yoruba: Mo wá ní kó gbàyè ọjọ́ díẹ̀ níbi iṣẹ́ kó lè kà á parí.
example_english: So I suggested that he take a few days off to complete his reading

example_yoruba: Síwájú sí i, bá a bá ń ṣiṣẹ́ àṣekára, a máa rówó fi ran àwọn ẹlòmíì lọ́wọ́.
example_english: Additionally, our hard work enables us to be generous in a financial way
